just like mom,

260
00:13:15,145 --> 00:13:18,436
and I'd never even think
about abandoning my children!

261
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:21,311
Girl 1: You love mom very much,
don't you, Conny?

262
00:13:21,395 --> 00:13:22,728
