with little bunny's help!

269
00:13:51,436 --> 00:13:52,770
Don: Conny.

270
00:13:53,936 --> 00:13:55,228
( Conny whimpers )

271
00:13:55,311 --> 00:13:56,811
I don't want to leave you!

272
00:13:56,895 --> 00:13:58,936
I want to stay right here!

273
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:01,686
Don: Conny, I'll miss you!

274
00:14:01,770 --> 00:14:02,395
