at the gate were still on.

287
00:14:54,478 --> 00:14:56,103
Mom hasn't come back yet either,

288
00:14:56,186 --> 00:14:58,561
so I don't think
Conny's left just yet.

289
00:14:58,645 --> 00:15:00,395
- Norman: Let's hurry, Emma.
- ( Emma grunts )

290
00:15:02,853 --> 00:15:04,436
