the gate or the fence."

292
00:15:14,770 --> 00:15:17,561
Norman: Yeah, I know.
We'll both get in trouble later.

293
00:15:20,978 --> 00:15:22,228
Emma: Conny?

294
00:15:28,936 --> 00:15:31,353
( Liquid dripping slowly )

295
00:15:47,686 --> 00:15:49,020
Emma: Is that the truck

296
00:15:49,103 --> 00:15:51,020
