in real life.

298
00:15:55,728 --> 00:15:56,603
Eh?

299
00:16:06,103 --> 00:16:06,978
Norman: Hmm.

300
00:16:15,561 --> 00:16:17,020
No one's here.

301
00:16:17,103 --> 00:16:19,686
Emma: Maybe she'll find it
if we leave it in here.

302
00:16:19,770 --> 00:16:20,811
Norman: Yeah, maybe.

303
00:16:25,770 --> 00:16:27,103
Eh?

304
00:16:27,186 --> 00:16:29,061
( Emma shuddering )

