( Gasps )

309
00:17:00,936 --> 00:17:02,811
( Liquid dripping )

310
00:17:05,395 --> 00:17:06,561
- Man: Is someone there?
- ( Both gasp )

311
00:17:09,061 --> 00:17:10,811
Man: Hey, did you
hear voices just now?

312
00:17:10,895 --> 00:17:13,353
Man 2: It's your imagination.

313
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:18,936
( Shuffling )

314
00:17:19,020 --> 00:17:20,895
( Door creaking )

315
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:25,936
Man 1: If it was a stray cat,

316
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:27,395
I would have
caught it for dinner.

317
00:17:27,478 --> 00:17:29,478
Man 2: You eat
those disgusting things?

318
00:17:29,561 --> 00:17:31,395
( Heavy footsteps )

319
00:17:35,020 --> 00:17:35,895
( Emma gasps )

320
00:17:35,978 --> 00:17:38,270
