00:17:40,186 --> 00:17:42,853
( Norman gasps )

322
00:17:42,936 --> 00:17:43,853
( Emma gasps )

323
00:17:46,978 --> 00:17:48,686
( Male demon hisses )

324
00:17:48,770 --> 00:17:50,686
( Laughs )
It looks so delicious.

325
00:17:50,770 --> 00:17:53,895
Human flesh
is definitely the tastiest.

326
00:17:53,978 --> 00:17:54,853
Norman: No.

327
00:17:57,270 --> 00:17:59,311
- ( Liquid sloshing )
- Demon 1: Damn!

328
00:17:59,395 --> 00:18:01,395
I wish I could have
just a fingertip.

329
00:18:01,478 --> 00:18:04,186
Male demon 2: Don't joke.
It's valuable merchandise,

330
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:06,770
definitely not something
we are meant to enjoy.

331
00:18:06,853 --> 00:18:10,020
The human flesh from this farm
is the highest quality.

332
00:18:10,103 --> 00:18:11,978
Only the rich can afford it.

333
00:18:13,436 --> 00:18:14,186
( Emma whispering ) Where's mom?

334
00:18:14,270 --> 00:18:15,145
Norman: Shh.

335
00:18:17,270 --> 00:18:18,895
Demon 3: How's the gupna?

336
00:18:18,978 --> 00:18:20,770
Demon 2: It's mostly done, sir.

337
00:18:20,853 --> 00:18:23,103
Demon 3: Another six-year-old.

338
00:18:23,186 --> 00:18:26,020
We've only been shipping out
average ones lately,

339
00:18:26,103 --> 00:18:27,520
but we'll be harvesting

340
00:18:27,603 --> 00:18:29,895
some of the high-grade stock
soon enough.

341
00:18:29,978 --> 00:18:32,186
- Right, Isabella?
- Isabella: Yes.

342
00:18:32,270 --> 00:18:33,978
Demon 3: These three
with full marks

343
00:18:34,061 --> 00:18:36,103
