353
00:19:10,311 --> 00:19:12,645
We're all just food?

354
00:19:12,728 --> 00:19:14,270
( Norman panting )

355
00:19:14,353 --> 00:19:15,645
Emma: It can't be.

356
00:19:15,728 --> 00:19:18,728
Didn't everyone go
to foster homes?

357
00:19:18,811 --> 00:19:23,270
And mom is a normal,
loving mother, right?

358
00:19:23,353 --> 00:19:26,020
This is all a mistake!
What we saw wasn't Conny!

359
00:19:26,103 --> 00:19:27,728
How could it be?!

360
00:19:39,145 --> 00:19:40,770
Norman: I'm afraid it was Conny.

361
00:19:40,853 --> 00:19:42,478
( Emma sobbing )

362
00:19:45,103 --> 00:19:47,020
( Wailing )

363
00:19:47,103 --> 00:19:48,728
( Wails echoing )

364
00:19:50,603 --> 00:19:52,186
Ray: Welcome home. How'd it go?

365
00:19:54,895 --> 00:19:56,311
Norman: We didn't
make it in time.

366
00:19:56,395 --> 00:19:58,270
( Stairs creaking )

367
00:19:59,395 --> 00:20:01,520
( Woman humming melody )

368
00:20:01,603 --> 00:20:04,186
